quran[9]{c,v,t,f}:
  11,91,"Wọ́n wí pé: “Ṣu‘aeb, a kò gbọ́ àgbọ́yé ọ̀pọ̀lọ́pọ̀ nínú ohun tí ò ń sọ. Dájúdájú àwa sì ń rí ọ ní ọ̀lẹ láààrin wa. Tí kò bá jẹ́ pé nítorí ti ẹbí rẹ ni, àwa ìbá ti kù ọ́ lókò pa; ìwọ kò sì lágbára kan lórí wa.”"
  11,92,"Ó sọ pé: “Ẹ̀yin ìjọ mi, ṣé ẹbí mi ló lágbára lójú yin ju Allāhu? Ẹ sì sọ Allāhu di Ẹni tí ẹ kọ̀yìn sí! Dájúdájú Olúwa mi ni Alámọ̀tán nípa ohun tí ẹ̀ ń ṣe níṣẹ́."
  11,93,"Ẹ̀yin ìjọ mi, ẹ máa ṣe bí ẹ ti fẹ́ nínú ẹ̀sìn yín, dájúdájú èmi náà yóò máa bá ẹ̀sìn mi lọ. Láìpẹ́ ẹ̀yin yóò mọ ẹni tí ìyà máa dé bá, tí ó máa yẹpẹrẹ rẹ̀, (ẹ̀yin yó sì mọ) ta ni òpùrọ́. Nítorí náà, ẹ máa retí. Dájúdájú èmi náà wà pẹ̀lú yín tí mò ń retí (ìkángun ọ̀rọ̀ yín).”"
  12,52,"(Yūsuf sọ pé): “Ìyẹn nítorí kí ọba lè mọ̀ pé dájúdájú èmi kò jàǹbá rẹ̀ ní ìkọ̀kọ̀. Àti pé dájúdájú Allāhu kò níí fi ìmọ̀nà síbi ète àwọn oníjàǹbá."
  12,53,"Èmi kò sì fọra mi mọ́ (níbi èròkérò); dájúdájú ẹ̀mí kúkú ń pàṣẹ èròkérò (fún ẹ̀dá) ni àfi ẹni tí Olúwa mi bá kẹ́. Dájúdájú Olúwa mi ni Aláforíjìn, Àṣàkẹ́-ọ̀run.”"
  12,54,"Ọba sọ pé: “Ẹ mú (Yūsuf) wá fún mi. Èmi yóò ṣe é ní ẹni ẹ̀ṣà lọ́dọ̀ mi.” Nígbà tí ọba bá a sọ̀rọ̀ tán, ó sọ pé: “Lọ́dọ̀ wa ní òní dájúdájú ìwọ ni ẹni pàtàkì, olùfọkàntán.”"
  13,19,"Ǹjẹ́ ẹni tí ó mọ̀ pé òdodo kúkú ni n̄ǹkan tí wọ́n sọ̀kalẹ̀ fún ọ láti ọ̀dọ̀ Olúwa rẹ, ó wa dà bí ẹni tí ó fọ́jú (nípa rẹ̀ bí)? Àwọn onílàákàyè ló ń lo ìrántí."
  13,20,"(Àwọn ni) àwọn tó ń mú àdéhùn Allāhu ṣẹ. Àti pé wọn kì í tú àdéhùn."
  13,21,"(Àwọn ni) àwọn tó ń da ohun tí Allāhu pa láṣẹ pé kí wọ́n dàpọ̀ pọ̀. Wọ́n ń páyà Olúwa wọn. Wọ́n sì ń páyà aburú ìṣírò-iṣẹ́."